Package: clinss
Type: Package
Title: Sample Size and Power Calculations for Clinical Trials
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Your", "Name", email = "you@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Sample size and power calculations for clinical trials,
    organized by endpoint, design, and hypothesis (superiority,
    non-inferiority, superiority by a margin, and equivalence). All
    methods are implemented from primary published formulas (e.g.,
    Julious (2004) <doi:10.1002/sim.1783>; Chow, Shao, and Wang (2008,
    ISBN:9781584889823)) using base R only, and every procedure is
    validated against published results and independent implementations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: stats
Suggests: 
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
